  "detailed_description": "<strong>Astrumis - Survive Together</strong> is an <u>exclusively co-op</u> horror game designed for two players. One player controls a survivor on an abandoned spaceship and the other the ship itself. They must work together to navigate the ship, solve puzzles & minigames and survive against the mysterious monster. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/956cc011622b80c3332da2560548d7b9.poster.avif?t=1754557577\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/956cc011622b80c3332da2560548d7b9.webm?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/956cc011622b80c3332da2560548d7b9.mp4?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE SURVIVOR</h2>Play as <strong>the survivor - John Kowalski</strong>. Walk around the ship and come face to face with the invisible monster. Heed instructions from the other player on how to avoid it and stay alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.poster.avif?t=1754557577\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.webm?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.mp4?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MISSION CONTROL</h2>Play as <strong>mission control - Yang Sungbin</strong>. Even though the monster is invisible to the naked eye, security cameras can reveal his location. Take control of them to help the other player navigate the spaceship safely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.poster.avif?t=1754557577\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.webm?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.mp4?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOP CHALLENGES</h2>Solve a variety of cooperative minigames. None can be completed alone, each requires you to work together with the other player.<br><br><br><br><i>Inspired by games like <strong>A Way Out</strong> and <strong>Keep Talking and Nobody Explodes</strong> - this project is made by a single developer in Unreal Engine 5, so please be patient, any updates will take time.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Astrumis - Survive Together</strong> is an <u>exclusively co-op</u> horror game designed for two players. One player controls a survivor on an abandoned spaceship and the other the ship itself. They must work together to navigate the ship, solve puzzles & minigames and survive against the mysterious monster. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/956cc011622b80c3332da2560548d7b9.poster.avif?t=1754557577\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/956cc011622b80c3332da2560548d7b9.webm?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/956cc011622b80c3332da2560548d7b9.mp4?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE SURVIVOR</h2>Play as <strong>the survivor - John Kowalski</strong>. Walk around the ship and come face to face with the invisible monster. Heed instructions from the other player on how to avoid it and stay alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.poster.avif?t=1754557577\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.webm?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.mp4?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MISSION CONTROL</h2>Play as <strong>mission control - Yang Sungbin</strong>. Even though the monster is invisible to the naked eye, security cameras can reveal his location. Take control of them to help the other player navigate the spaceship safely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.poster.avif?t=1754557577\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.webm?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924860/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.mp4?t=1754557577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOP CHALLENGES</h2>Solve a variety of cooperative minigames. None can be completed alone, each requires you to work together with the other player.<br><br><br><br><i>Inspired by games like <strong>A Way Out</strong> and <strong>Keep Talking and Nobody Explodes</strong> - this project is made by a single developer in Unreal Engine 5, so please be patient, any updates will take time.</i>",
